1 A BILL for an Act to amend and reenact section 54-11-16 of the North Dakota Century Code,
2 relating to criminal history record checks by the state treasurer for individuals with access to
3 federal tax information.
4 BE IT ENACTED BY THE LEGISLATIVE ASSEMBLY OF NORTH DAKOTA:
5 SECTION 1. AMENDMENT. Section 54-11-16 of the North Dakota Century Code is
6 amended and reenacted as follows:
7 54-11-16. Criminal history record checks.
8 The state treasurer shall require any applicant, employee, or independent contractor who
9 has access to federal tax information to submit to a statewide and nationwide criminal history
10 record check, and subsequent recheck within tenfive years from the date of the previous
11 criminal history record check. The nationwide criminal history record check must be conducted
12 in the manner provided by section 12-60-24.
